sequenceDiagram
    participant App as AppMobile
    participant GPS as LocationService
    participant Buffer as RouteBuffer
    participant API as RouteController
    participant DB
    participant AdminWeb
    participant Admin
    App->>GPS: StartTracking()
    loop Mỗi 5 giây
        GPS-->>App: {lat, lng, accuracy, timestamp}
        App->>Buffer: Append(point)
    end
    Note over Buffer: Khi buffer đạt 20 điểm hoặc 2 phút
    Buffer->>API: POST /api/route/batch {deviceId, userId?, points[]}
    API->>DB: INSERT BULK RouteLog
    DB-->>API: ok
    API-->>Buffer: 201
    Buffer->>Buffer: Clear()
    Note over Admin: Admin xem heatmap
    Admin->>AdminWeb: Mở trang Route Analytics
    AdminWeb->>API: GET /api/route/heatmap?from=&to=
    API->>DB: SELECT lat,lng,COUNT(*) GROUP BY grid
    DB-->>API: heatmap data
    API-->>AdminWeb: json
    AdminWeb-->>Admin: Hiển thị heatmap lên Leaflet
